    <h1>Text Formatting Tags</h1>
    <p>This is a <strong>Strong</strong> and <i>emphasized</i> text.</p>
    <p>Use <b>Bold</b>, <em>Italic</em>, <u>Underline</u>, and <mark>Mark.</mark></p>
    <p>Here is <code>inline code</code> and <strike>strikethrough</strike>.</p>
    <p>This is <small>small</small>, <sub>subscript</sub>, and <sup>superscript</sup>.</p>
    <p>Below is a blackquote example.</p>
    <pre>       Performatted</pre>
    <pre>       text example</pre>
    <p> <u>WHO</u>is an abbreviation</p>
